oor dog parks across California. Search by city, neighborhood, or zip to discover safe, climate-controlled play spaces for your dog.\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org\",\"mainEntity\":{\"@type\":\"ItemList\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org#itemlist\",\"numberOfItems\":20,\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"name\":\"A Bark Above Pet Salon\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/a-bark-above-pet-salon\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Roanoke\",\"addressRegion\":\"VA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"name\":\"A Bark Away NJ\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/a-bark-away-nj\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Jersey City\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"name\":\"A Barkery Unleashed\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/a-barkery-unleashed\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Everett\",\"addressRegion\":\"WA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"name\":\"AJ Country Kennel\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/aj-country-kennel\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Lemoore\",\"addressRegion\":\"CA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":5,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"name\":\"All American Pet Resorts North Brunswick\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/all-american-pet-resorts-north-brunswick\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"North Brunswick Township\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":6,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"Sport