owners. This facility features climate-controlled facilities for North Carolina's varied weather, caring and attentive team members, offering pet care. Their services creates a safe, climate-controlled environment. centrally located for Wake Forest residents. Experience the difference at Audrey's Barkyard\",\"slug\":\"audreys-barkyard\",\"address\":\"3129 Heritage Trade Dr\",\"street\":\"3129 Heritage Trade Dr\",\"city\":\"Wake Forest\",\"state\":\"NC\",\"zipCode\":\"27587\",\"full_address\":\"3129 Heritage Trade Dr, Wake Forest, NC 27587, USA\",\"latitude\":35.952606,\"longitude\":-78.5179677,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJl7bO4jKAqYkRpHS4Eu-IzD4\",\"phone\":\"(919) 435-8491\",\"website\":\"http://audreysbarkyard.com/\",\"rating\":4.7,\"reviewCount\":258,\"userRatingsTotal\":258,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:00 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"4:00 – 6:00 PM\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{},\"photos\":[{\"url\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/audrey-s-barkyard/audrey-s-barkyard-1.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"},{\"url\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/audrey-s-barkyard/audrey-s-barkyard-2.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"}],\"photo\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/audrey-s-barkyard/audrey-s-barkyard-1.jpg\",\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJb6_WrQ9fwYkRCp3ETlo9qsE\",\"name\":\"Bag of Bones Barkery\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"$10\",\"slug\":\"bag-of-bones-barkery\",\"address\":\"364 NJ-33\",\"street\":\"364 NJ-33\",\"city\":\"Hamilton Township\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"08619\",\"full_address\":\"364 NJ-33, Hamilton Township, NJ 08619, USA\",\"latitude\":40.23391669999999,\"longitu